<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.981.53583.figure39>
    dc:description "Figure 39. Type species of alycaeid genus-group taxa A Pincerna constricta (Benson, 1851), syntype (NHMUK 1906.4.4.41; type species of Cycloryx) B Pincerna liratula (Preston, 1907), syntype (NHMUK 1907.5.20.191; type species of Pincerna) C Stomacosmethis sarasinorum (Bollinger, 1918), lectotype (NHMB 2411. a; type species of Stomacosmethis). Photographs: Harold Taylor (A, B); Eduard Stoeckli (C)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/468684" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.981.53583.figure40>
